<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-earth">on earth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong><a href="在">可用于否定词或最高级后，以加强语气</a>世界上；(在) 人间：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is nothing great but man on earth; there is nothing great but mind in man. 
世界上最伟大的是人类，而人类最伟大的是思想。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm the luckiest man on earth.
我是世上最幸运的人。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[常用于疑问词后加强语气] 究竟；到底：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Why on earth</strong> do you need a phone?
你到底为什么要一部手机？</p><footer>2012 全国</footer></div></div>